2008-12-06
Adventure Chess 0.039 delivered
Bugs fixed:
- Queen move from left edge to right edge of board.
- Check in three moves.
Features:
- A little engine tuning.

2008-11-23
Adventure Chess 0.031 delivered
Bugs fixed:
- Castling under check.
- Knight check from edges of the board.
- Wall checking during knight, rook, queen and king moves fixed
Features:
- Time of engine thinking measurement added.

2008-11-20
Adventure Chess 0.028 delivered - this is first "playable" version of the game
